00:00:21,120 --> 00:00:25,180
 in planning poker each estimator which should be everybody on the team 

7
00:00:25,580 --> 00:00:30,440
is holding a set of cards that contain the numbers the team has agreed to use as their estimates 

8
00:00:30,780 --> 00:00:33,620
normally this will be the modified Fibonacci sequence

9
00:00:33,800 --> 00:00:35,260
