15
00:00:51,500 --> 00:00:54,660
once each team member has decided upon an estimate

16
00:00:54,820 --> 00:00:56,840
they pulled that card out of their hand 

17
00:00:56,940 --> 00:00:58,900
holding it so no one else can see it

18
00:00:59,120 --> 00:01:00,700
when everyone has picked an estimate

19
00:01:00,840 --> 00:01:03,220
the cards are revealed all at the same time

20
00:01:03,400 --> 00:01:06,280
if everyone is holding up the same number we're done

21
00:01:06,520 --> 00:01:09,240
write that number down as the estimate and move on

22
